texts.text: There are two sizes of chest rooms. None of their chests have loot.
One vindicator spawns in each room.
The oak wood slabs on Layers 3, 5 and 7 are upside down.

All of the flower pots have blue orchids.
All of the oak wood slabs are upside down.
Any flowers on top of the flowerpot is what you put in the flower pot.
